INSERT INTO `client_spotlights` VALUES (3,'Mick Morgan\'s St. Patrick\'s 5K','Charity Race','2013-04-09 15:31:49','2013-04-10 18:29:11','<p>\"The t-shirts came out better than I imagined &ndash; and I knew they would be great! - but when I saw them for the first time I couldn&rsquo;t believe how terrific they looked! Same t-shirt quality as last year&rsquo;s shirt &ndash; except One Billion Shirts saved our organization a lot of money per shirt AND they made a donation to HESSCO Elder Services &ndash; talk about a win &ndash; win situation! The true testimony &ndash; only the first 500 runners to sign up for our 5K received a t-shirt &ndash; the comments heard after our race &ldquo; did you check out the t-shirts &ndash; next year I will sign up sooner!\"<br /><br /> Mary Long<br /> Director of Communications&nbsp;and Fund Development<br /> HESSCO Elder Services/Mick Morgan&rsquo;s St.<br /> Patrick&rsquo;s 5K</p>'),(4,'SCSU Men\'s Basketball','NCAA Basketball','2013-04-09 15:38:19','2013-04-09 15:38:19','<p>&ldquo;The shirts came out great, we saved some much needed money and getting a Thank You note from St. Jude&rsquo;s was amazing, it inspired us all to think of giving back more often. We love the concept, keep up the good work!&rdquo; -</p>\r\n<p>Michael Makubika, Assistant Men&rsquo;s Basketball Coach, Southern Connecticut State University</p>'),(5,'Boston Burger Company','Restaurant','2013-04-09 15:43:10','2013-04-09 15:43:10','<p>The Boston Burger Company is one of the hottest burger joints in Boston and for good reason. &nbsp;Not only do they have great burgers but the wait staff is in top of the line American Apparel custom t-shirts!</p>'),(6,'Wealthy Knowledge','Small Clothing Brand','2013-04-09 15:47:20','2013-04-09 15:47:20','<p>Wealthy Knowledge is a small clothing brand that makes clothes for its owner to wear and as an entrepreneur to get shirts printed in a small run, save money, and donate to Kiva.org and help other entrepreneurs is a win-win for all!</p>'),(7,'Thinking Cup','Coffee Shop','2013-05-22 23:26:07','2013-05-22 23:26:07','<p>Thinking Cup not only keeps our staff caffeinated during the day with their premier Stumptown Coffee blends but also leverages their T-shirt orders to donate money to The Wounded Warrior Foundation. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>'),(8,'Flour Bakery','Bakery','2013-05-22 23:32:06','2013-05-22 23:32:06','<p>Great food, gracious service, warm atmosphere, heady aromas, and irresistible displays is a great way to sum up Flour Bakery. &nbsp;Unbelievable choices not only with their food, drinks, and decor but Flour even makes conscious decisions on their screen printed aprons, donating money back to Share Our Strength to ensure no kid goes hungry!</p>'),(9,'Cafe Vittoris','Coffee Shop','2013-05-22 23:34:53','2013-05-22 23:34:53','<p>If you\'ve ever visited Boston, I can assure you that you have either had a cup of coffee or witnessed others enjoying a cup at this legendary establishment. &nbsp;Cafe Vittoria is world renowned as the first Italian caffe in Boston. &nbsp;These quality t-shirts &amp; polo shirts directed benefited the American Institute for Cancer Research!&nbsp;</p>'),(10,'Horizons For Homeless Children','Charity Race / Walk','2013-05-22 23:38:08','2013-05-22 23:38:08','<p>Horizons For Homeless Children is an amazing Boston based charity organization dedicated to improving the lives of young homeless children and their families. &nbsp;When their 3rd annual Route for Kids 5k was approaching we handled their order with care, saved the organization money, volunteered at the race, and donated money back to the charity, the ultimate win-win for all parties involved!</p>');
