INSERT INTO `pages` VALUES (1,'about','<div class=\"slider_hold\" style=\"height: auto;\">\r\n<div class=\"slider_text\">\r\n<h1 style=\"width: 634px;\">We consider this a profit <span>sharing</span> initiative.</h1>\r\n<p>Get high quality shirts, save money, and help change the world!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--slider_text ends--></div>\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"img_det_txt\">\r\n<div class=\"abt_list m_top_75\">\r\n<h1>Our Mission:</h1>\r\n<p>Create a socially conscious way for customers to purchase t-shirts by donating 25&cent; from our profit a charity of the customers choice. Through this slight shift we will create an industry standard that will redirect millions to charities and change the world forever!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--abt_list ends-->\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>Why T-shirts?</h1>\r\n<p>The scope of this industry is massive and the product is becoming commoditized. With 1 Billion units per year, a slight shift can create a huge impact. All print shops use the same blank shirts, same inks, and same techniques. The only difference is the profit margin.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--abt_list ends-->\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>How Can We Do It?</h1>\r\n<p>We run an industry leading screen print company and through technology, strategic partnerships, and experience, we can print your t-shirts and save you money while providing a fast turnaround and quality product. Once customers are aware of this, they will begin pushing other screen print companies to join this movement which will create a tidal wave of wealth to charity.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--abt_list ends-->\r\n<div class=\"abt_list_im\">\r\n<h1>Why Work With Us?</h1>\r\n<p>The big secret is that there is no secret. We will print your shirts the same way using the same shirt and the same ink as your current vendor. We will give you the best price and when printing with us you will have the opportunity to choose your favorite charity and we will donate money to them on your behalf.</p>\r\n<p>The donation comes from our profit and we will beat or match your current price, allowing you to simply leverage your order to help redirect money to those that need it most!</p>\r\n<img src=\"../../../assets/about_img.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<!--abt_list_im ends-->\r\n<div class=\"abt_list_im1\">\r\n<h1>How It Works:</h1>\r\n<p>Your need to order t-shirts and you visit our website. First you choose the charity which you want to donate to. You then fill out our Order Form and we review your order and provide the best possible price and send you back a quote. If it makes sense to work with you, we go forward with your order. Once paid for, we take 25&cent; per shirt from our profit and donate to your charity of choice on your behalf. We will send you the receipt and most charities will send you their own Thank You note.</p>\r\n<p>Once order is placed and deadline is set, we order the blank shirts and print them in our 150,000 square foot facility. Once printed, the shirts undergo quality control and once passed are shipped to you before the deadline!</p>\r\n<p>You now have your shirts, saved money on your order, and donated to charity. That is a win-win!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--abt_list_im1 ends--></div>\r\n</div>','2013-03-25 15:05:10','2013-03-25 15:28:10'),(2,'ccc','<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"ccc_hold\">\r\n<div class=\"order_text\">\r\n<div class=\"ccc_head\">\r\n<h1>College<span>Charity</span>Challenge</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--order_head-->\r\n<div class=\"ccc_txt_det\">\r\n<p>The College Charity Challenge is an opportunity for college students to experience a high intensity startup working side by side with founders, top tier sales managers, mentors, and industry decision makers. This is a live situation with real decisions and consequences.</p>\r\n<p>The College Charity Challenge by OneBillionShirts.org is an 8 week fast paced challenge in which student teams of 5 will compete to raise money for charities through a new socially conscious way of doing business.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--ccc_txt_det ends-->\r\n<div class=\"ccc_how_works\"><span>How it works:</span>\r\n<p>Each team will consist of 5 students who will be given 100 charities to work with. Teams will use sales &amp; marketing strategies in order to raise money for their selected charities through the sale of custom t-shirts. At the end of the contest, the teams combined charitable donations will be tallied. OBS will match each teams charitable contributions split equally amongst team members. The winning team will receive 2x their contributions up to a maximum of $50,000.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--ccc_how_works ends-->\r\n<div class=\"ccc_chlng_det\"><span>Challenge Details:</span>\r\n<p>- Duration: 8 weeks (March 1 - May 1)</p>\r\n<p>- Compensation: Contest is an unpaid internship</p>\r\n<p>- Prize money: We will match each teams charitable contribution and winning team will receive 2x up to $50,000.</p>\r\n<p>- Training: Initial 2 hour training session along with 2 hour optional weekly meetings.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--ccc_chlng_det ends-->\r\n<div class=\"ccc_app_process\"><span>Application Process - Deadline February 22nd:</span>\r\n<p>- All students will complete application through www.onebillionshirts.org/ccc</p>\r\n<p>- Teams will be picked by OBS staff</p>\r\n<p>- Teams will be announced through website and participating students and teachers will be emailed and called further instructions</p>\r\n<p>- Initial meet &amp; greet and training will be held on March 4th at OBS offices in Downtown Boston</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--ccc_chlng_det ends-->\r\n<div class=\"ccc_app_process\"><span>Criteria For Applicants:</span>\r\n<p>- Must be able to travel to downtown Boston once per week</p>\r\n<p>- Phone, computer, and internet connection</p>\r\n<p>- Willingness to learn and expand their knowledge and skills</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--ccc_chlng_det ends-->\r\n<div class=\"ccc_app_process\"><span>The Challenge:</span>\r\n<p>- Teams will collaborate using Asana, a leading task management tools used by most leading tech companies</p>\r\n<p>- Teams will assign roles consisting of: sales, marketing, and management</p>\r\n<p>- One team member will be assigned team manager each week and will be in charge of communicating progress</p>\r\n<p>- OBS staff and mentors will be available to team members through emails, phone calls, and in person meetings.</p>\r\n<p>- Teams will raise money by selling t-shirts in which OBS donates 25&cent; per shirt to charity</p>\r\n<p>- Teams will work closely with the charities to leverage their existing sphere of influence to create a new avenue of fundraising</p>\r\n<p>- Contest gives students an inside look on the startup phase of an actual business and will be fast paced with real decisions and consequences.</p>\r\n<p>- Teams can develop new strategies and materials which will have to be approved by OBS before using but will be kept proprietary to that group while contest is live, allowing teams to create a competitive advantage.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--ccc_chlng_det ends--></div>\r\n<!--ccc_hold ends--></div>\r\n<!--ccc_hold ends-->\r\n<div class=\"btn_align\">\r\n<div class=\"choose_btn_2\"><a href=\"http://www.formstack.com/forms/?1395609-duqAcxM5BW\">Apply Now</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','2013-03-25 15:05:10','2013-03-25 15:28:42'),(3,'how_it_works','<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"order_form_hold\">\r\n<div class=\"order_text\">\r\n<div class=\"order_head\" style=\"width: 726px;\">\r\n<h1>You can <span>impact</span> the world <br /> with your next order.</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--order_head-->\r\n<p>Use your next order to redirect money to those that need it most.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--order_text ends-->\r\n<div class=\"works_imgs_holder\">\r\n<div class=\"img_portion\">\r\n<div class=\"img_text_lft pad_1\">\r\n<div class=\"big_img\"><img src=\"../../../assets/w_img_1.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"big_img_text\">\r\n<p>You need t-shirts for an event, party, promotion, etc.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--big_img_text ends--></div>\r\n<!--img_text_lft ends-->\r\n<div class=\"border_bottom\">\r\n<div class=\"border_bot\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<!--border_bot ends--></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--img_portion ends-->\r\n<div class=\"img_portion\">\r\n<div class=\"img_text_lft pad_1\">\r\n<div class=\"big_img_text m_lft\">\r\n<p>Search our exclusive charity database or suggest your own charity for us to donate to.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--big_img_text ends-->\r\n<div class=\"big_img_rit\"><img src=\"../../../assets/w_img_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<!--big_img_rit ends--></div>\r\n<!--img_text_lft ends-->\r\n<div class=\"border_bottom\">\r\n<div class=\"border_bot\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<!--border_bot ends--></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--img_portion ends-->\r\n<div class=\"img_portion\">\r\n<div class=\"img_text_lft pad_1\">\r\n<div class=\"big_img\"><img src=\"../../../assets/w_img_3.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"big_img_text\">\r\n<p>We will print your shirts and donate a minimum of 25&cent; per shirt to the charity of your choice.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--big_img_text ends--></div>\r\n<!--img_text_lft ends-->\r\n<div class=\"border_bottom\">\r\n<div class=\"border_bot\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<!--border_bot ends--></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--img_portion ends-->\r\n<div class=\"img_portion\">\r\n<div class=\"img_text_lft pad_1\">\r\n<div class=\"big_img_text m_lft\">\r\n<p>Your t-shirts arrive. You received the same shirt, better price, and helped a charity help others!.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--big_img_text ends-->\r\n<div class=\"big_img_rit\"><img src=\"../../../assets/w_img_4.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<!--big_img_rit ends--></div>\r\n<!--img_text_lft ends-->\r\n<div class=\"border_bottom\">\r\n<div class=\"border_bot\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<!--border_bot ends--></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--img_portion ends-->\r\n<div class=\"img_portion\">\r\n<div class=\"img_text_lft pad_1\">\r\n<div class=\"big_img\"><img src=\"../../../assets/w_img_5.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"big_img_text\">\r\n<p>You have your t-shirts and raised money and awareness for your favorite charity! That\'s a win-win!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--big_img_text ends--></div>\r\n<!--img_text_lft ends--></div>\r\n<!--img_portion ends--></div>\r\n<!--works_imgs_holder ends--></div>\r\n<!--order_form_hold ends--> <!--<div class=\"btn_align\">--> <!--<div class=\"choose_btn_2\">--> <!--<a href=\"/charities\">Choose Your Charity</a></div>--> <!--</div>--></div>','2013-03-25 15:05:10','2013-03-26 13:53:35'),(4,'our_story','<div class=\"slider_hold\" style=\"height: auto;\">\r\n<div class=\"slider_text\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<!--slider_text ends--></div>\r\n<!--slider_hold ends-->\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"img_det_txt\">\r\n<div class=\"abt_img_t\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<!--abt_img_t ends-->\r\n<div class=\"abt_sto_txt\"><center>\r\n<h1><span>There are well over 1 Billion custom t-shirts printed each year and with our simple concept, we can change the world!</span></h1>\r\n</center>\r\n<p><strong> Charities save lives, let me tell you!</strong><br /><br /> Without charities and the people who support them, I can almost certainly tell you that I would not be here with you today. In 1999 I was saved from the Kosovo war and brought to America as a refugee at age 14. <br /><br /> I was only a kid living what I thought to be a normal life until one day everything changed. Lives were lost, homes destroyed, and childhoods stolen. <br /><br /> Imagine going to bed at night wondering if you are going to live to see tomorrow? Hard to picture, right? That was life for me until one day I was saved by people I&rsquo;ve never met before. With the help of truly good people from different charitable organizations, I got a second chance at life and made a promise to make it worthwhile!<br /><br /> <a href=\"http://www.compleopartners.com/images/fort-dix-article.pdf\">Click here to read an article from my first 2 weeks in America</a><br /><br /> <strong>T-shirts? Why T-shirts?</strong><br /><br /> Back in 2012 while working for Morgan Stanley I knew I was ready to jump ship and start a company that would help make the world a better place, I just did not know what I was going to do yet. Explaining my passion and vision to my friend Greg Berry, an executive in the custom apparel industry, he said he would love to give back in some way also and we set up a meeting to talk again.<br /><br /> When we met he had an idea that can change the world. When he said T-shirts, my reaction was &ldquo;T-shirts? Why T-shirts?&rdquo;...<br /><br /> T-shirts! How many t-shirts do you own? How many t-shirts are being worn right now in this building? Everybody has multiple T-shirts and will be getting more this year, what better vehicle to touch millions of lives? I was a bit taken back but my viewpoint on custom t-shirts changed dramatically that day. He was right, the product is omnipresent and the market is ripe for disruption!<br /><br /> As we all use the same blank shirts, same ink, and same print techniques, we can offer customers a win-win situation by allowing them to save money &amp; help others at the same time. <br /><br /> <strong>Ok, I\'m in...</strong><br /><br /> Greg brought previous successes, suppliers, vendors, an established print shop, and expertise and I brought with me a burning desire to make good on my promise from 1999; make my second chance at life worthwhile and provide the same opportunity to as many people as I could. <br /><br /> <strong> What do we name the company?</strong><br /><br /> After several failed attempts at a company name, we finally sat down and determined that we wanted a company that can last forever and a name that would act as a star in the sky assuring that although we may get lost at points, we always know what direction we&rsquo;re heading.<br /><br /> OneBillionShirts.org signifies the massive scale of this concept and industry while also reminding us that we cannot do it alone. A .org is meant for collaboration and we understand that we cannot print 1 billion shirts per year. Just as McDonald&rsquo;s set the bar with The Dollar Menu, we want to turn this industry into a way to redirect wealth to those that need it most, industrywide. <br /><br /> If every shirt printed has a portion of the proceeds directed to charity this simple shift will have a huge effect on the world, which is why we all need to work together to successfully implement this change.<br /><br /> <strong>What\'s Next?</strong><br /><br /> Within months of inception we already worked with some of the top businesses, individuals, and charities in the Boston area and will soon be expanding nationwide. One day very soon the bar will be set and I will be able to proudly look back and although I will never remember each person individually that helped my family and I, I&rsquo;ll be able to say that I repaid my debt to them and made good on my promise to make my second chance at life worthwhile!<br /><br /> Cheers,<br /><br /> <img src=\"http://compleopartners.com/images/Albion-Signature.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /> Albion Calaj, co-founder</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<center><!--abt_sto_txt ends--> <!--abt_sto_txt ends--></center></div>\r\n<!--img_det_txt ends-->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!--<div class=\"btn_align\">-->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!--<div class=\"choose_btn_2\">-->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!--<a href=\"/charities\">Choose Your Charity</a></div>-->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!--</div>--></div>','2013-03-25 15:05:10','2013-05-22 18:24:27'),(5,'top_ten_reasons','<div class=\"slider_hold\" style=\"height: auto;\">\r\n<div class=\"slider_text\">\r\n<h1 style=\"font-size: 46px; width: 700px;\">Top 10 reasons to work with us.</h1>\r\n<p>Our mission is much larger than t-shirts!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--slider_text ends--></div>\r\n<!--slider_hold ends-->\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"img_det_txt\">\r\n<div class=\"abt_list m_top_75\">\r\n<h1>10. Quality Shirts &amp; Fast Turnaround</h1>\r\n<p>We print using the same blank shirts, same inks and same print techniques as every other large scale printer in the world</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--abt_list ends-->\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>9. Spread Goodness</h1>\r\n<p>Our mission is to raise more money and awareness for charities around the world to allow them to do what they do best, change the world!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--abt_list ends-->\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>8. Show That You Care</h1>\r\n<p>We present you with a choice. Print with us and redirect money to charity or use another vendor and just get your shirts printed. Working with us shows that you care.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--abt_list ends-->\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>7. Join The Movement</h1>\r\n<p>We promote you and each other through our network and together we all rise to the top.</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/about_img.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>6. Promote Giving</h1>\r\n<p>When your employees, associates, and stakeholders see you leverage this opportunity, they will be more conscious of opportunities and chances to give back.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--abt_list_im ends-->\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>5. Help People You Care About</h1>\r\n<p>When we donate from our profit, it is not to a cause we choose. We donate from our profit to a cause in which you choose. This puts money directly in the hands of those you care about and believe in.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>4. Save Money</h1>\r\n<p>Our promise is that we will beat or match your current prices and still donate from our profit. If that is not the case, it may not be the best fit to work with us. We only want to create a win-win for all.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>3. Be The Change</h1>\r\n<p>We all want to make the world a better place. By working with us you are directly raising money for a charity and indirectly helping to create a snowball effect. The bigger the snowball, the bigger the change!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>2. Lead By Example</h1>\r\n<p>Those around you will see that you are taking advantage of every opportunity to promote goodness in your world. This shows others to be more aware of opportunities around them and will create a domino effect.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"abt_list\">\r\n<h1>1. It Just Makes Sense!</h1>\r\n<p>You are simply placing the same order as usual and by doing so donating money directly to a charity of your choice and joining a movement set out to leave the world a better place, a total win-win!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--abt_list_im1 ends--></div>\r\n<!--img_det_txt ends--></div>','2013-03-25 15:05:10','2013-03-26 13:44:57');
